OL,3,CRestrained and called a liar: ARFID
OL,4,Cpatient's treatment after wrong
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FBy Rachel Dixon, ITV News Multimedia
OL,8,FProducer
OL,10,FAfter being diagnosed with an eating
OL,11,Fdisorder, Ellen Macpherson hoped she
OL,12,Fwould get the treatment she needed to
OL,13,Frecover. Instead she was restrained,
OL,14,Fsedated, and called a liar.
OL,16,FWhen now-qualified Dr Macpherson
OL,17,Fdrastically lost weight while studying
OL,18,Fmedicine at St Andrews University, she
OL,19,Fwas temporarily pulled from her course
OL,20,Fand diagnosed with anorexia, she tells
OL,21,FITV News.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/15
