OL,7,FFigures, assessed for Eating Disorders
OL,8,FAwareness Week (26 February ` 3 March
OL,9,F2024), found in 2018 Beat's Helpline
OL,10,Freceived 295 calls for support with
OL,11,FARFID, or 2% of total calls.
OL,13,FBy 2023, this Beat received 2054 calls
OL,14,F- or 10% of its total calls for the
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FThere's very few treatment centres in
OL,18,Fthe UK specifically for ARFID and its
OL,19,Fleft some people waiting years for
OL,20,Fdiagnosis and help.
