OL,7,FUnlike anorexia, it isn't driven by
OL,8,Ffeelings about weight and shape.
OL,10,FInstead it revolves around fear about
OL,11,Feating due to distressing experiences
OL,12,Fwith food, or lack of interest or
OL,13,Fsensory issues around the texture or
OL,14,Ftaste of certain foods.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/15
