OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FDue to this key difference, Ms
OL,8,FMacpherson left her six month stay in
OL,9,FThe Priory at Cheadle Royal Hospital
OL,10,Fin Manchester, where she was wrongly
OL,11,Ftreated for anorexia, feeling her
OL,12,F"self-confidence, self-worth, and
OL,13,Fpsychological wellbeing post admission
OL,14,Fwas much worse than before I went in".
OL,16,FShe told ITV News: "There was a lot of
OL,17,Fmiscommunication so they were getting
OL,18,Freally frustrated and angry with me
OL,19,Fand then I was panicking.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/15
