OL,7,F"It just escalated the situation, into
OL,8,Fending up with being sedated and
OL,9,Frestrained.
OL,11,F"I wasn't in a place where people
OL,12,Fwould've trusted my judgment at all.
OL,13,FIf I had decided, this is the reason
OL,14,Fwhy I'm scared to have this, and they
OL,15,Fwould not have believed me for a
OL,16,Fsecond. I would've been able to tell
OL,17,Fthat and become really, really
OL,18,Fdistressed. I realized pretty quickly
OL,19,Fnot to say the truth."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/15
