OL,4,Cpatient's treatment after wrong
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"The interpersonal dynamic there is
OL,8,Fextremely disruptive to you as an
OL,9,Findividual because, being in the care
OL,10,Fof people who you can tell think
OL,11,Fyou're a liar is horrific.
OL,13,F"It does something to you
OL,14,Fpsychologically that I can't describe.
OL,15,F'
OL,17,F"You start to think, am I a liar? Am I
OL,18,Fthe person they say I am? Am I a bad
OL,19,Fperson?"
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
