OL,7,FThe Priory told ITV News that ARFID,
OL,8,Fis "complex and heterogeneous",
OL,9,Fmeaning there are a wide range of
OL,10,Fpossible underlying causes and
OL,11,Fphysical symptoms.
OL,13,FAs such, every patient is assessed and
OL,14,Ftreated based on their own individual
OL,15,Fneeds, by a multi-disciplinary team,
OL,16,Fthey said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/15
