OL,7,FThe Priory also added it used sedation
OL,8,Fand nasogastric feeding under the
OL,9,FMental Health Act, when people with
OL,10,Feating disorders become very
OL,11,Fphysically unwell due to severe weight
OL,12,Floss and can be at risk of dying.
OL,14,FIf you've been impacted by this story
OL,15,Fplease get in contact via .
OL,17,FFor help with ARFID, or any eating
OL,18,Fdisorders contact Beat .
