OL,7,FMs Macpherson was previously wrongly
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with anorexia aged in 2012,
OL,9,Fover 12-years-later she was diagnosed
OL,10,Fwith Autism and this led to her being
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with ARFID.
OL,13,FDespite this, except from medical
OL,14,Finterventions where she was tube fed
OL,15,Fto stop her dying from malnutrition,
OL,16,FMs Macpherson has never been given
OL,17,Fpsychological help with her disorder.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/15
