OL,7,FShe believes if she was diagnosed as a
OL,8,Ftoddler, and if there were more
OL,9,Fspecialists, she would not be in this
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,FOf the estimated 55 NHS Trusts or
OL,13,FCommunity Interest Companies which
OL,14,Fprovide eating disorder services for
OL,15,Fadults, 38 NHS providers (78%) were
OL,16,Funclear as to whether any of them
OL,17,Fwould be able to support ARFID
OL,18,Fpatients, according to eating disorder
OL,19,Fcharity Beat.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/15
