OL,7,FFor children and young people, 44
OL,8,F(80%) were unclear on their websites
OL,9,Fas to whether any of them provide or
OL,10,Fsupport treatment for patients with
OL,11,FARFID.
OL,13,FThe lack of services contributed to
OL,14,Fthe death of seven-year-old son Alfie,
OL,15,Ffrom Stockport, died suddenly after a
OL,16,Fseverely restricted diet left him
OL,17,Fmalnourished in December 17, 2021.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/15
