OL,7,FHis mother Lucy Morrison's said she
OL,8,Ftried to get help countless times but
OL,9,FArfid was only diagnosed after his
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FStockport NHS Foundation Trust has
OL,13,Fsince apologised and made changes.
