OL,7,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "During the
OL,8,Fpandemic, referrals for eating
OL,9,Fdisorders for children increased by
OL,10,Falmost 50% and the NHS is clear that
OL,11,Fimproving care for people with an
OL,12,Feating disorder including ARFID is
OL,13,Fvital, with investment, targeted
OL,14,Fsupport and training helping to
OL,15,Fdevelop community eating disorder
OL,16,Fteams in all areas in England.
